# M9 Memory OS — Knowledge 文档 + agent/memory 模块化 + 生产级持久化

## 里程碑

**M9** — LangGraph checkpointer 从 `MemorySaver` 升级为 `AsyncPostgresSaver`；新增 `conversations` / `chat_messages` 业务表；`agent/memory/` 作为 Memory OS 总入口（RAG 经 facade 重导出）。

## 关联 Skill

| Skill | 用途 |
|-------|------|
| [entity-service](../Skills/entity-service/SKILL.md) | conversations / chat_messages 模型与服务 |
| [add-api-endpoint](../Skills/add-api-endpoint/SKILL.md) | `GET /conversations` |
| [http-integration-test](../Skills/http-integration-test/SKILL.md) | conversations_test、跨轮/重启验收 |
| [db-migrate](../Skills/db-migrate/SKILL.md) | `003_chat_history.py` |
| [local-dev](../Skills/local-dev/SKILL.md) | PostgreSQL + Milvus 本地验收 |
| [extract-ai-knowledge](../Skills/extract-ai-knowledge/SKILL.md) | `docs/knowledge/memory-os.md` |

## 范围

### 交付文件

| 文件 | 说明 |
|------|------|
| `docs/knowledge/memory-os.md` | 9 类 Memory、五阶段流水线、5 种压缩方案、BillMind 映射 |
| `agent/memory/**` | Memory OS 总入口：working / chat / profile / knowledge / semantic / pipeline / planned |
| `agent/memory/working/checkpointer.py` | `AsyncPostgresSaver` 生命周期 |
| `server/model/conversation.py` | `conversations` + `chat_messages` |
| `server/service/conversation.py` | CRUD + `append_turn` |
| `server/api/conversations.py` | `GET /conversations`、`GET /conversations/{thread_id}/messages` |
| `server/alembic/versions/003_chat_history.py` | 聊天历史迁移 |
| `agent/graph/agent.py` | 使用 `get_checkpointer()` |
| `server/main.py` | lifespan 初始化/关闭 checkpointer |
| `server/api/agent.py` | invoke 后 `append_turn` |

### 不在范围内

- Redis Working Memory / Neo4j / ClickHouse
- Extraction / Integration / Forgetting 自动化（pipeline stub only）
- 5 种压缩方案 LLM 实现（文档 + stub）
- HITL 断点（M12）

