## 运行命令

```bash
docker compose up -d
.venv/bin/pip install -r requirements.txt
.venv/bin/python3.14 server/main.py
.venv/bin/python3.14 -m pytest server/api/agent_test.py server/api/conversations_test.py agent/memory -v
```

## 验收标准

- [ ] `AsyncPostgresSaver` 替代 `MemorySaver`，重启后会话可恢复
- [ ] `POST /agent/chat` 后 `GET /conversations/{thread_id}/messages` 含 user/assistant
- [ ] `memory_status()` 反映 postgres / milvus 状态
- [ ] `docs/knowledge/memory-os.md` 存在且 README 索引已更新
